OL,5, One of Australia's highest-profile TV  
OL,6, hosts, Stan Grant, has stood down from 
OL,7, presenting a prime-time show after     
OL,8, receiving "relentless" racist abuse.   
OL,10,FGrant said he had always endured racism
OL,11,Fin his career but it had escalated     
OL,12,Fafter he covered the King's Coronation 
OL,13,Ffor national broadcaster ABC.          
OL,15,FThe veteran Aboriginal journalist had  
OL,16,Fspoken during the coverage about the   
OL,17,Fimpact of colonisation on his people.  
OL,19,FThe ABC has called for the "grotesque" 
OL,20,Fabuse against the host to stop.        
